I'm not able to change the order of the scores that appear on the result page of https://hc18.grand-challenge.org/evaluation/results/.

When you go to Admin->Evaluation Settings->Extra results columns: I fill in: 
{"Std absolute difference (mm)": "aggregates.absolute_difference.std","Mean difference (mm)": "aggregates.difference.mean", "Std difference (mm)": "aggregates.difference.std", "Mean DICE (%)": "aggregates.DICE.mean","Std DICE (%)": "aggregates.DICE.std", "Mean Hausdorff distance (mm)": "aggregates.hausdorff_distance.mean", "Std Hausdorff distance (mm)": "aggregates.hausdorff_distance.std"}

But when I save this, the order automatically changes to:
{"Std DICE (%)": "aggregates.DICE.std", "Mean DICE (%)": "aggregates.DICE.mean", "Std difference (mm)": "aggregates.difference.std", "Mean difference (mm)": "aggregates.difference.mean", "Std Hausdorff distance (mm)": "aggregates.hausdorff_distance.std", "Mean Hausdorff distance (mm)": "aggregates.hausdorff_distance.mean", "Std absolute difference (mm)": "aggregates.absolute_difference.std"}
